===============================================================================
Joint Calibration
===============================================================================

This package performs joint astrometry across multiple visits of the same field.
It will eventually be extended to also perform joint photometry at the same time.

It was derived from lsst_france/meas_simastrom

Old readme notes below (to be deleted when no longer relevant):

Prerequites
===========

We should use C++11

at CCIN2P3:

to get version g++ 4.9.1:

  export PATH=/opt/rh/devtoolset-3/root/usr/bin:${PATH}

This package needs **micro_cholmod**

This code successfully compiles using g++ 4.8, 4.9 and clang 3.5

